Would he now like to try his hand at replacing the dangerous kerb at 408
Glasgow Road, Paisley?
After it caused a nasty fall I reported it on May 5, 1991, to Mr Marchetti,
Divisional Manager in Paisley, and a reminder was sent on November 2, 1994, all
